  ¡§Lan2 ti7 kou2-cha2 hou7 toa7-chui2 lau5-khi3 e5 ji7 chit-pang Ki-tok-kau3 e5 sian-siN u7 koh ka3 lan2. Ia7 u7 ka3-si7 lan2 thiN e5 sin5 chhong3-cho7 ban7-mih8 kap lan2 lang5 e5 kou3-su7, long2 si7 lan2 sou2 m7-bat thiaN chin ho2 e5 su7.¡¨ Ko2-hong e5 chhoan-tiuN2 lai5 hu3 kang2-sip8-hoe7 2 jit8, sui5-si5 u7 tng2-khi3 ka-ti7 e5 hoan-sia7 po3 ho2 e5 siau-sit. Koe3 cha2-khi2 chiu7 koh lai5 hu3, kau3 thau3-boe2 chin ti3-i3 lai5 thiaN. 
  In khi2-seng e5 i3-su3 si7 ai3 oh8-ji7, tan7-si7 lan2 u7 iong7 Chhong3-se3-ki2 e5 kou3-su7 kap Ia-sou e5 lai5 lek8 kong2 hou7 in thiaN. Teh kong2 e5 si5 lan2 u7 iong7 Seng3-keng kap ang-a2-tou5 hou7 in khoaN3. Chin sim-sek in e5 oe7 ¡§siong7¡¨ kap ¡§tou5¡¨ si7 iong7 siang7-khoan2 e5 ji7 ¡§xalingo¡¨ chit-ku3-oe7. An2-ni thang chai in khoaN3 Seng3-keng e5 tou5 tu2-tu2 si7 chhin-chhiuN7 khoaN3 sia2-chin e5 khoan2. Sou2-i2 in thiaN e5 kou3-su7 u7 chhim-chhim tiau5-ti7 in e5 thau5-khak. Tui3 chit-tiap8 khi2 lan2 ti7 soaN-te7 kong2 to7-li2 khah siong5 u7 iong7 ang-a2-tou5. In-ui7 in si7 chhin-chhiuN7 gin2-a2 ai3 khoaN3 sui2 e5 ang-a2, koh ia7 khah e7 ki3-tit lan2 e5 sou2 kong2, siang7-si5 in khah boe7 siuN7 li2 sou2 kong2 e5 si7 khang-khang e5 oe7. 
  Kang2-sip8-hoe7 e5 tiong-kan lan2 ia7 u7 ka3 in chin che7 in e5 oe7 e5 seng3-si. Ti7 im-gak8 e5 si5-kan i2-goa7 ti7 khai-si2 iah-si7 hioh-khun3, iah-si7 lan2 chhoa7 in le2-pai3 e5 si5 siong5-siong5 u7 gim5-si, chit-e5 ia7 chin toa7 pang-chan7 in e5 sin3-giong2. 
  An2-ni kau3-hoe7 e5 lou7-boe2-jit8 koat-sim-hoe7 e5 si5 in u7 kong2 khi2-seng in si7 kan-ta siuN7 ai3 lai5 oh8 in e5 ji7, kau3-taN chin chai Ki-tok e5 to7-li2 si7 chin-ho2, beh kiu3 in e5 lang5, beh chhoa7 in kiaN5 ti7 chin-chiaN3 e5 lou7. Sou2-i2 in long2 u7 koat-sim beh tng2-khi3 po3 chit-khoan2 e5 ho2 siau-sit hou7 in e5 lang5 thiaN. 
  Koh bo5 chin-ku2, lan2 ia7 u7 iong7 in e5 oe7 in3 chit-pun2 Na2-a2 toa7-chui2 e5 kou3-su7, lai5 chi2-beng5 in toa7-chui2 e5 kou3-su7 u7 m7-tioh8. Kau3 1951 ni5 lan2 e5 Bunun oe7 e5 Ma2-thai3 hok-im-su ia7 i2-keng tui3 Hiong-kang2 e5 Seng3-keng kong-hoe7 chhut-pan2. Ti7 1952 ni5 5 goeh8 lan2 ia7 koh tui3 Tai5-lam5 Kong-po3-sia7 chhut-pan2 in e5 seng3-si kiong7 u7 108 siu2. Lan2 ia7 ng3-bang7 koh bo5 kui2-ni5, in u7 thang iong7 in e5 oe7 thak8 Sin-iok choan5-pou7 e5 seng3-keng. 
  Bunun e5 ji7, pang-chan7 in e5 seng-oah8 chin toa7. In m7-na7 tui3 che thang thak8-chheh, ia7 thang sia2-phoe kap ki3-siau3. I2-cheng5 in-ui7 ai3 kong2 1 ku3-oe7, u7-si5 kiaN5 3 jit8 e5 lou7, hian7-chai7 sin3 Chu2 e5 lang5 long2 si7 iong7 Lo5-ma2-ji7 e5 phoe teh kou-thong. U7 1 pai2 iu5-kiok8 e5 lang5 theh8 Lo5-ma2-ji7 e5 phoe khi3 Sin3-gi7-hiong kong-sou2 mng7 siu-phoe e5 lang5 tiam3-ti7 ta2-loh8? In thau5-pai2 khoaN3-tioh8 chit-ho7 e5 phoe sui5-si5 to7 kong2: ¡§Chit-khoan2 Eng-kok-ji7 hoan-a2 thai2 e7-hiau2 thak8?¡¨ Au7--lai5 kio3 hit lang5 lai5 mng7, khoaN3 i e7 thak8 e5 si5 tak8-ke toa7 gong5-ngiah8. 
  Seng3-sin5 E5 He2 Sio SoaN-te7 
  Li2 bat khoaN3-kiN3 he2 sio soaN bo5? Ti7 ou-am3 e5 mi5-si5 tui3 hng7 e5 sou2-chai7 lan2 bat khoaN3-kiN3 soaN-teng2 kui-phian3 teh toh8 e5 he2. Khi2-seng si7 chit8 sou2-chai7, au7-lai5 he2 ka-ki7 sio kau3 pat8-ui7, chit8-tiap8-a2 ku2 chiu7 moa2-soaN long2 si7 he2. Seng3 Sin5 ti7 san-te7 choe3 kang tu2-tu2 chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni. Tek8-piat8 ti7 chit e5 ou-am3 m7-sin3 e5 si5-tai7 lan2 tui3 hng7-hng7 e5 piN5-toe7 lai5 khoaN3 Seng3 Sin5 e5 he2 ti7 soaN-teng2 teh toh8 e5 khoan2-sit, boe7-bian2-tit hou7 lan2 e5 sim oe7 kam2-kak sio. 
  Ti7 1949 ni5 chhun-thiN ti7 Giok8-li2 khui e5 Seng3-keng kang2-sip8-hoe7 khak-sit8 u7 chin toa7 e5 hau7-ko2. Lai5 hu3-hoe7 12 e5 Bunun e5 chheng-lian5 u7 siu7 toa7 e5 kam2-kek, khng3 toa7 e5 ng3-bang7 ti7 in e5 sim-lai7 soaN3-hoe7. Hit-si5 in e5 sin3-giong2 i2-keng u7 Seng3 Sin5 e5 he2 teh toh8, chhin-chhiuN7 gou7-sun5-choeh hit-si5 e5 hak8-seng, in e5 sim na7 bo5 kan-cheng3 to7-li2 chiu7 tong3-boe7-tiau5. Ti7 kang2-sip8-hoe7 soah hit am3, in tiong-kan 3 lang5 chiu7 khi3 Chheng-chui2 choe3 kian3-cheng3, kong2 khi2 in ti7 Giok8-li2 sou2 tit-tioh8 e5 to7-li2. 
  Lai5 hu3 Kang2-sip8-hoe7 e5 lang5 te7-it chhut-tioh8 e5 chiu7-si7 Kou2-hong e5 chhoan-tiuN2 Taliban. I tng2-khi3 liau2-au7 ti7 chit8 ni5 au7 u7 in2-chhoa7 70 lang5 lai5 sin3 Chu2, koh u7 khi2 Bunun thau5 chit8-keng e5 pai3-tng5. Hian3-tng5-sek e5 si5 chin seng7-hong2, Sun Bok8-su tiau-kang tui3 Tai5-pak lai5 hu3 sek. In tai7-ke ia7 chin hoaN-hi2, thai5-ti pan7 toh lai5 chhiaN2 piN5-toe7 san-toe7 iok u7 200 lang5 e5 hiaN-ti7. Koh ia7 tah-piN5 ti7 goa7-khau2, thiau3-bu2 kap choe3-hi3, lai5 piau2-hian7 in e5 hoaN-hi2. 
  I2-goa7 lai5 hu3 kang2-sip8-hoe7 e5 lang5 tng2-khi3 ia7 long2 u7 choe3 chin ho2 e5 kang ti7 ka-ki7 e5 hoan-sia7. 2 ni5 au7 ti7 Lun5-thian, Takimi, Chheng-chui2 ia7 u7 khi2 pai3-tng5. Toh-khe u7 70 lang5 e5 chu7-hoe7 ti7 Giok8-li2 e5 pai3-tng5, Lun5-san ia7 u7 60 lang5 e5 chu7-hoe7 ti7 Taiyal e5 pai3-tng5. Chiah e5 Bunun e5 sin3-tou5 u7 e5 u7 khi3 pat8 e5 hoan-sia7 choe3 kian3-cheng3, kau3 1952 ni5 Toh-khe hiong e5 Tiong-peng5 kap Ban-li2 hiong e5 Ma2-oan2 ia7 u7 khi2 pai3-tng5. 
  SaN-chiN Thian-kok 
  Ti7 1951 ni5 e5 ni5 be2, tui3 Tang-pou7 u7 nng7 e5 chheng-lian5 kiaN5 3 jit8 e5 lou7 poaN5-soaN peh-nia2 kau3 Sin-ko-soaN kha te7-it koan5 e5 Tong-pou e5 hoan-sia7. In e5 mia5 si7 Topas kap Laong. In u7 toa3 toa7-pak e5 ang-a2-tou5, chiau3 chit e5 lai5 kong2 Ku7-iok kap Ia5-sou e5 kou3-su7 hou7 Bunun thiaN. Ia7 u7 ka3 in Bunun e5 Lo5-ma2-ji7 kap Seng3-si. Chiah e5 long2 si7 in tui3 kou2-cha2 kau3 hian7-kim long2 m7-bat thiaN, m7-bat khoaN3 tioh8 e5 sin e5 tai7-chi3. Hit am3 e5 chu7-hoe7 u7 300 lang5. In tui3 am3-thau5 chiu7 chu7-chip8, na2 chhiuN3 Seng3-si na2 khoaN3 ang-a2-tou5 thiaN to7-li2 kap oh8 ji7. In-ui7 tak8 hang7 long2 si7 sin e5, sou2-i2 hoe7-chiong3 long2 boe7 sian7, kong2 e5 lang5 koh-khah si7 an2-ni. Kau3 koe thi5 e5 si5 in chiah chai i2-keng chin oaN3. Hit-si5 Topas kong2, ¡§TaN tioh8 hioh-khun3, kiaN-liau2 siuN am3 oe7 eng2-hiong2 lin2 bin5-a2-jit8 e5 kang.¡¨ 
  ¡§Boe7, boe7, goan2 long2 boe7 ai3-khun3, tioh8 koh ka3 goan2, goan2 m7 si3-soaN3, bin5-a2-chai3 e5 tai7-chi3 bo5 iau3-kin2.¡¨ 
  ¡§Goan2 iau2 beh ti7 chia nng7 am3, m7-si7 bo5 ki-hoe7, sou2-i2 tioh8 hou7 goan2 hioh-khun3.¡¨ 
  ¡§Kau3 bin5-a2 am3 siuN ku2,¡¨ u7 kui2-na7 lang5 toa7-siaN kong2, ¡§Tioh8 the2-thiap goan2 kiaN5-lou7 chin sian7. Tioh8 hou7 goan2 hioh-khun3 kau3 bin5-a2 cha2-khi2 chiah koh kong2.¡¨ 
  Tui3 an2-ni hoe7-chiong3 chiah kam-goan7 soaN3. Kau3 ke3 cha2-khi2 cha2-cha2 chiu7 chin choe7 koh chu7-chip8 lai5 beh thiaN. Chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni e5 jiat8-sim in thiaN 2 jit8 3am3 chiu7 long2 koat-sim beh sin3 Chu2. 
  In tiong-kan chit8 e5 50 hoe3 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 mia5 kio3 Oli, thiaN tioh8 kong2 lan2 lang5 e5 choe7 kap Ia5-sou e5 chin2-kiu3, siu7 chin toa7 e5 kam2-kek. I tui3 siau3-lian5 chiu7 siong5-siong5 kau3 piN5-toe7 kap Tai5-oan5 lang5 choe3 phaiN2, sou2-i2 Tai5-oan5-oe7 chin gau5 kong2. I siu7 sia3-bian2 te7-it choe7 sou2-i2 te7-it thiaN3 Chu2, iau2 chit8 nng7 e5 sian-siN toa3 ti7 i e5 chhu3, chin ho2 khoan2-thai7 in. 
  Tui3 chia li7 saN tiam2-cheng e5 lou7 e5 pat8 sou2-chai7 kio3 Bong7-hiong e5 chhoan-tiuN2 u7 thiaN-tioh8 chit e5 siau-sit, ti7 te7-saN jit8 chiu7 phai3 lang5 lai5 ngia5-chih Topas kap Laong. Hit am3 ti7 hia u7 200 lang5 lai5 thiaN in e5 ka3-si7. Kau3 thiN beh kng koe thi5 e5 si5 2 e5 sian-siN u7 siuN7 beh hioh-khun3, na7-si7 chhoan-tiuN2 kap lau7-lang5 long2 m7 hou7 in hioh. In nng7 lang5 khoaN3-kiN3 200 lang5 e5 jiat8-sim, kou-put-chiong koh soa3-chiap kong2 to7-li2 kau3 thiN-kng. 
  Tng-si5 Sin3-gi7-hiong e5 tak8 sou2-chai7 i2-keng oh8 Tai5-oan5-lang5 pai3 kong-ma2-pai5. Keh-jit8 chhoan-tiuN2 Kulisima tui3 in kong2, ¡§Cha-mi5 goan2 u7 thiaN lin2 ka3-si7 chin Sin5 e5 to7-li2, taN i2-keng chai goan2 tui3 piN5-toe7-lang5 oh8 e5 pang e5 sin5 si7 m7-tioh8 e5. TaN li2 khoaN3 pang-a2 e5 sin5 ti7 chia, chhiaN2 lin2 ka7 goa2 theh8 hiat-kak8.¡¨ 
  Tui3 an2-ni Laong chiu7 chhut chhiu2 theh8 hit-te3 kong-ma2-pai5 kiaN5 kau3 khah hng7 tek-pho7 e5 sou2-chai7 hiat ti7 hia. U7 chit8 e5 lau7-lang5 tui3 lang5 kong2 an2-ni choe3 Laong e5 pak-tou2 tek-khak oe7 thiaN3. Chong2-si7 khoaN3 Laong long2 bo5 an2-choaN2 chiu7 kong2, ¡§Sit8-chai7 u7 chin e5 Sin5 teh po2-hou7 in.¡¨ Tui3 an2-ni hit chhoan choan5-pou7 tit-tioh8 kiu3. 
  Ti7 khah ke7 e5 sou2-chai7, tai7-iok chit8-tiam2-cheng e5 lou7 e5 Kiu2-bi2 e5 lang5 ia7 u7 thiaN-kiN3 ho2 e5 siau-sit, chai-iaN2 te7-saN-jit8 beh khi3 in e5 sou2-chai7, chiu7 cha2-cha2 phai3 kui2-na7 e5 chheng-lian5 lai5 ngia5-chih in nng7 lang5. Na7-si7 Bong7-hiong e5 Bunun lu2-chu2 chheng-lian5 kui2-na7 lang5 thiaN-kiN3 in e5 sian-siN, lang5 beh chhoa7-khi3 chiu7 koaN2-kin2 chau2-khi3, theh8 sian-siN e5 heng5-li2 khi3 chhang3 ti7 pat8-ui7. Tui3 an2-ni nng7 peng5 teh saN-chiN thian-kok. (Ma2-thai3 11:12) 
  In koh ti7 Kiu2-bi2, Sin3-gi7, Sin-hiong, Hong-kong, chiah e5 sou2-chai7 chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni po3-thoan5 chin2-kiu3 e5 hok-im. 
  Tak8-ui7 u7 200 lang5 e5 chu7-hoe7, tak8-am3 na7 bo5 koe-thi5 bo5 thang khun3. Soan-to7-su na7 beh khi3 pat8 sou2-chai7 e5 si5, tiaN7-tioh8 u7 kui2-na7 lang5 toe3 in khi3 pat8-ui7 koh thiaN in e5 ka3-si7. 
  In ti7 Hong-kong (Toyoka) e5 si5 u7 chit8 e5 Bunun e5 tai7-jin5 mia5 kio3 Laong chu7-chip8 cheng3-lang5 lai5 phai3-chhut-sou2 thiaN to7-li2. I thiaN to7-li2 liau2-au7 u7 mng7 Soan-to7-su kong2, ¡§I2-cheng5 lan2 e5 chou2-kong u7 ka7 lan2 kong2 lang5 si7 tui3 se3-se3 e5 thang5 lai5 pian3, u7 e5 kong2 si7 ka-chau2 lai5 pian3, an2-ni lan2 lang5 chin bo5 ke3-tat8. TaN u7 thiaN li2 kong2 si7 Siong7-te3 chhong3-cho7, si7 I e5 kiaN2, goa2 e5 sim chin hoaN-hi2. Chong2-si7 li2 sou2 kong2 e5 m7-chai si7 chin-sit8 a2-m7-si7? Si7 li2 ka-ki7 siuN7 e5 a2-si7 lek8-su2 e5 chheh u7 sia2?¡¨ Hit-si5 Soan-to7-su chiu7 eng7 Chhong3-se3-ki2 hou7 i khoaN3. I chin hoaN-hi2, chiu7 sin3 in e5 chhui3 sou2 chhut tak8-ku3 e5 oe7. Hit-am3 in m7-kheng2 hou7 Soan-to7-su khun3, thiaN to7-li2 kau3 thiN-kng. Kau3 beh si3-soaN3 e5 si5, thau5-lang5 Tiban chiu7 kong2, ¡§TaN goan2 koat-teng7 beh hok8-sai7 Siong7-te3, tui3 bin5-a2-jit8 khi2 chiu7 beh khi2 pai3-tng5, kau3 lin2 khi3 pat8-ui7 koh tng2-lai5 chia chiu7 oe7 ho2.¡¨ Ko2-jian5 in tui3 ke3-jit8 chiu7 khi3 chho3 chhiu7-a2 lai5 khi2 pai3-tng5. Chit e5 chiaN5-choe3 Se-pou7 thau5-chit8-keng Bunun e5 pai3-tng5. 
  In nng7-lang5 koh loh8 khah ke7 e5 sou2-chai7, Lai7-hm5-pou e5 hoan-sia7. Ti7 hia iu5-goan5 siu7 siang7-khoan2 e5 hoan-geng5. Ke3-jit8 in-ui7 in 20 jit8 ku2 bo5-mi5 bo5-jit8 ke3-thau5 choe3 kang e5 koan-he7 Topas i2-keng peh boe7 khi2-lai5. I e5 sin-khu chin sio na2 kun2-chui2, choan5-sin long2 thiaN3. In u7 lang5 chiu7 khi3 kio3 i-seng, na7-si7 i-seng khi3 pat8-ui7 tioh8 kui2-na7-jit8 chiah oe7 tng2-lai5. In chin hoan5-lo2 kiaN-liau2 sian-siN oe7 si2, siuN7 kau3 bo5 hoat-tou7 chiu7 khi3 kio3 in e5 tang5-ki lai5 beh koaN2-kui2. Tang5-ki lai5 e5 si5 chiu7 kio3 Topas khi2-lai5, beh ka7 i koaN2-kui2. Topas tioh8-chit8-kiaN, chiu7 ka7 in kong2 lan2 bo5 sin3 chit-khoan2, tioh8 ki5-to2 ThiN Pe7. I toa7-siaN ki5-to2 chiu7 koh khun3. Kau3 hit-am3 i e5 jiat8 long2 the3, koh khia7 ti7 cheng3-lang5 e5 bin7-cheng5 kong2 to7-li2. Cheng3-lang5 toa7 gong5-ngiah8 kong2, ¡§Chin-chiaN3 Sin5 u7 pang-chan7 i.¡¨ Chhin-chhiuN7 Boat8-tai7-liap8 e5 Ma2-li7-a toe3 Chu2, u7 chit8 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 tui3 Sin3-gi7 toe3 in lai5 e5 Obao khoaN3-kiN3 chit e5 sin5-jiah chiu7 tng2-khi3 cheng5 sou2 thoan5 to7-li2 e5 tak8 e5 hiuN-sia7 po3-ko3 chit e5 su7, hou7 cheng3-lang5 e5 sin3-sim ke-thiN chit8-poe7 e5 jiat8. 
  Tng-si5 Bunun chok8 e5 Ia5-lou7-sat-leng2 Kou2-hong kau3-hoe7 u7 thiaN-kiN3 Seng3 Sin5 u7 toa7 io5-tang7, Sin3-gi7 hiong e5 lang5 chiu7 koh nng7 e5 lang5 koaN2-kin2 khi3 beh pang-chan7-thoan5-to2-li2 e5 kang. Chit8 e5 chiu7-si7 Bunun e5 Po2-lo5, mia5 Taliban, koh chit8 e5 chiu7-si7 Talima. Chit nng7 e5 lun7 sin3-giong2 kap leng5-lek8 si7 iaN5-ke3 cheng5 e5 lang5 kui2-na7 poe7. Lau5-thoan5 si7 ti7 chit chok8 te7-it hiong5-pian7, Talima si7 Seng3-keng te7-it chai, sou2-i2 in nng7 lang5 hou7 lang5 hoan-geng5 chhin-chhiuN7 thiN-sai3. In kau3 Lai7-hm5-pou bo5 kui2-jit8 chiu7 siau-sit thoan5 kau3 tak8 e5 hiuN-sia7. Tui3 tak8 e5 sou2-chai7 chiu7 phai3 lang5 lai5 chhiaN2, na7 bo5 lai5 chhiaN2 e5 sou2-chai7 in chiu7 bo5 thang khi3. U7 chit8 pai2 tui3 Langlun u7 phai3 tai7-piau2 lai5 Lai7-hm5-pou e5 sou2-chai7, kau3 e5 si5 chin siu7-khi3 me7 hia e5 Bunun kong2, ¡§Lin2 chin phaiN2-sim, u7 ho2 e5 mih8 khng3-bat8 kiaN lang5 chai, tui3 Kou2-hong lai5 e5 sian-siN tiaN7-tiaN7 khng3 ti7 lin2 chia ka3-si7 ia7 bo5 po3 goan2 chai.¡¨ Chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni in siong5-siong5 saN-chiN ai3 chhiaN2 sian-siN. Tui3 in khi3 hia choe3 kang liau2-au7 ti7 Langlun u7 tit-tioh8 500 lang5, ti7 Isingan u7 tit-tioh8 300 lang5 Tam-adoan u7 400 lang5, Walabi ia7 u7 200 mia5 sin3 Chu2. Tak8-sou2-chai7 cheng5 u7 sin3 e5, sin3-giong2 na2 kian-kou3, sin3 e5 lang5 ia7 na2 ke-thiN. 
